{"tid":331032,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"國際球會冠軍杯之我見","createTime":"2017-07-21T18:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T08:04:40.000Z","uid":107362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9a0e58e77866347aadb0b5e87e30639f6bfb34","tid":331032,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:18:04.000Z","msg":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既分組真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈曼攞冠軍有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班魚拉突 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先曼咩城,唔好玩啦 同市垃圾，3分已袋<br />\n<br />\n巴塞,,如果係0809巴狗就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到歐霸又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..曼半力夠WIN,又3分<br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地出青年軍練下is ok,又3分<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 魔獸,普巴,馬達,米希 加上關鍵王DDG.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n冠軍就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家歐超杯見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手魚拉突..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"dbb2ef55a58ffa12ac9fd7dfa573f3c97e84807d","tid":331032,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:19:28.000Z","msg":"吓  我地最連無對手..."},{"pid":"7dccb8f75cd26c14479c123808d488c02040fc43","tid":331032,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ac616f5e974eb6d401652fe66c0d672ac90bdd","tid":331032,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c8f86c3f346479aabc1a45e7ef10f40ad773f5","tid":331032,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:31:55.000Z","msg":"獌狗邊有踢冠軍杯牙？<br />\n恥笑開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951299c312f3bb0496017e75a82ca29be30eaf3c","tid":331032,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b513f7c28e603946f9a6651f2225c7c9175749","tid":331032,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"